\begin_layout Subsubsection*
(4)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Substitute (2) and (3) in the equations of the model:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(S)\,\,p_{t}=\kappa x_{t}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(D)\,\,p_{t}=-\frac{1}{\vartheta}x_{t}+e_{t}+\frac{1}{\vartheta}z_{t}
\]

