(7)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Find the equilibrium values.
 The nterest rate is 0 by the definition of the question, 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 has been already calculated above.
 The price level and the exchange rate are:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
e_{t}=p_{t}=\kappa x_{t}=\kappa z_{t}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
which is negative.
